475
00:51:55.965 --> 00:51:57.115
Je ne pars pas.

476
00:52:10.171 --> 00:52:11.871
Premier tiroir.

477
00:52:12.600 --> 00:52:13.469
Quoi ?

478
00:52:13.650 --> 00:52:16.520
Le premier tiroir...

479
00:52:18.184 --> 00:52:19.561
